metadata.name: Birb Fren #2
metadata.description:
Birb Frens is a collection of 24,727 randomly generated NFTs, made up of stylistic elements handcrafted by Squidbop.
Birbs can be strange, funny, kooky, serious or just downright weird. With a myriad of unique traits and almost infinite combinations every bird is completely unique.

Visit www.squidbop.com to learn more.
